    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823580/extras/57579f0ff4b776741e28dbbca17c3df6.poster.avif?t=1533129677\" width=500 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823580/extras/57579f0ff4b776741e28dbbca17c3df6.webm?t=1533129677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823580/extras/57579f0ff4b776741e28dbbca17c3df6.mp4?t=1533129677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>【时间的灰烬】<br>我是谁？为什么会在这个神秘的小岛上？带着这些疑惑，我将探索这个小岛的每一片地方，工厂工厂、轮船、小屋、火箭、灯塔...和每一个岛上的居民对话，有灯塔看守人、船票检查员、老奶奶、工厂研究员...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823580/extras/df6d02c6af858bc1b9feb444d0fed96f.poster.avif?t=1533129677\" width=500 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823580/extras/df6d02c6af858bc1b9feb444d0fed96f.webm?t=1533129677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823580/extras/df6d02c6af858bc1b9feb444d0fed96f.mp4?t=1533129677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>发现一个又一个秘密，当我获得开启时间机器的密码，我将了解这个小岛的前世今生，了解一段不为人知的往事...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823580/extras/7dc983a4ec9f80e81b4f8ab78ccc07db.poster.avif?t=1533129677\" width=500 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823580/extras/7dc983a4ec9f80e81b4f8ab78ccc07db.webm?t=1533129677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823580/extras/7dc983a4ec9f80e81b4f8ab78ccc07db.mp4?t=